Goal
- Write a professional but approachable email to my team explaining that our Q3 roadmap is delayed by 3 weeks due to a vendor delay, without blaming the vendor or the team, mentioning an upcoming mitigation plan with details pending, and clearly outlining what is changing and what remains the same.

Context
- Audience: internal team members
- Tone: professional but not overly corporate or stiff

Input
write an email to my team about our Q3 roadmap slipping by 3 weeks because of a vendor delay. keep it professional but not too corporate or stiff. dont blame the vendor or anyone on the team. mention we have a mitigation plan but i havent finalized the details yet. they need to know whats changing and what stays the same.